description: Retrieves a list of your run caches.

nested_items.name: items
nested_items.description: Details about each run cache in the response.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: Unique resource identifier for the run cache.

nested_items.name: cacheBehavior
nested_items.description: Default cache behavior for the run cache.

nested_items.name: cacheS3Uri
nested_items.description: The S3 uri for the run cache data.

nested_items.name: creationTime
nested_items.description: The time that this run cache was created (an ISO 8601 formatted string).

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The identifier for this run cache.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the run cache.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: Pagination token to retrieve additional run caches. If the response does not have a ``nextToken``value, you have reached to the end of the list.
